<div class="row">

    <div class="container" >
        <div class="portfolio-detail" >
            <div class="container">

                <div class="row" >
                    <div class="row space60"></div>
                    <div class="row space60"></div>
                    <div class="row" id="faq">
                        <div class="row space60"></div>
                        <div class="row space60"></div>
                        <div class="col-md-12 faq_bg" >
                            <!-- Nav Tabs -->
                            <div class="nav nav-tabs faq_content">
                                <div class="faq_scroll">
                                    <p>Click on each question below to show the answer. Scroll down for more questions:</p>
                                    <div class="block">
                                        <input type="checkbox" name="city" id="cityA"  />
                                        <label for="cityA">
                                            <span>What will I get if I register FREE?</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <div class="info">
                                            <p><span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">simply</span>weight’s basic registration is free. You will gain access to hundreds of medical weight loss articles, videos, tools, newsletters, blogs and more. However you will miss out on our exclusive 100-Day video tutorials for <span style="font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">sim</span>portion/<span style="font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">sim</span>aktiv/<span style="font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">sim</span>happy, webinars with Q&A and specialist advice and personalised support. In addition, you will not receive a personalised programme to suit your needs. You will need to subscribe to the 100-Day programme which suits you. You can pay using the following credit and debit cards: Delta, Solo, Maestro, Switch, Mastercard, paypal and Visa. All transactions will be processed through Worldpay, which is a secure payment service.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="block1">
                                        <input type="checkbox" name="city" id="cityB" />
                                        <label for="cityB">
                                            <span>How much does the 100-Day Programme cost?</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <div class="info">
                                            <p>You can register with <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">simply</span>weight or free but if you want to take advantage of our specialist, personalised programmes you will need to subscribe. The standard 100-Day <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">simply</span>weight programme is only £1 per day. We also have an Elite version of our 100-Day programme which includes continuous, 1-2-1 support from our medical team. The Elite programme costs £10 per day but places are limited due to the intensive nature of the programme and it’s requirements.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="block">
                                        <input type="checkbox" name="city" id="cityC" />
                                        <label for="cityC">
                                            <span>How is this programme different from other weight loss programmes?</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <div class="info">
                                            <p>People gain weight for a number of reasons. They may try and lose weight by reducing calories, exercising or doing both. However many people still don’t see the desired results despite their efforts. This may be due to underlying concerns such as hormonal/metabolic problems, psychological issues or a combination of both. <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">simply</span>weight is a revolutionary and unique programme as it is designed solely by doctors, endocrinologists, dietitians, physiotherapists, fitness trainers, psychologists and motivational experts. We know that there is no one-stop solution for your weight loss success, so we offer a personalised, individual service which addresses all aspects of your life (not just diet and exercise). This includes continuous guidance through daily tasks and tutorials and support in improving your confidence, self-esteem, hunger pattern, overcoming cravings, emotional eating and boosting your fitness level.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="block1">
                                        <input type="checkbox" name="city" id="cityD"  />
                                        <label for="cityD">
                                            <span>How much weight can I expect to lose in 100 days?</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <div class="info">
                                            <p>While it is possible to lose a significant amount of weight early in your programme, we recommend losing 1lb to 2lbs (0.5kg to 1kg) per week as a safe level of weight loss. The weight loss experienced depends on several factors including your basal metabolic rate, medical problems, activity, starting weight and medications. Therefore our recommended weight loss for 100 days will be different to your final goal weight. Ultimately, the amount of weight you end up losing depends largely on your commitment to the programme and how much you have to lose in the first place. Some people can safely lose up to 2 stones (around 14Kg) in 100 days.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="block">
                                        <input type="checkbox" name="city" id="cityE"  />
                                        <label for="cityE">
                                            <span>How does this programme work?</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <div class="info">
                                            <p>Once you register, we ask you to complete ‘My profile’ on your dashboard (<span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">sim</span>podium), which helps us to understand your background, history of medical problems, activity level, psychology, medications and previous weight loss attempts. Thereafter we prescribe a portion controlled meal plan which is displayed in your <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">sim</span>portion section. <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">sim</span>aktiv is your activity section which helps you stay active and burn any extra calories consumed. The most important section is <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">sim</span>happy, your own motivational guru. <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">sim</span>happy helps you overcome emotional eating, craving and also helps to improve your self-esteem and confidence. You also will be supported by our experts through forums, recorded webinars and will be advised on your medical conditions and/or medications. However our medical experts do not replace a face to face consultation with your doctor. Before making any changes you should ALWAYS consult your doctor.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="block1">
                                        <input type="checkbox" name="city" id="cityF"  />
                                        <label for="cityF">
                                            <span>Who can join <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">simply</span>weight, <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">simply</span>wazan and <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">diabesity</span>?</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <div class="info">
                                            <p>Anyone can join one of these programmes if you are overweight/obese and you are aged 18 years or older. We have specific programmes designed to prevent Type 2 Diabetes and for South Asian and Middle Eastern. These are the diabesity and <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">simply</span>wazan programmes respectively. People of African or Afro-Caribbean origin will benefit from joining the <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">simply</span>weight programme.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="block">
                                        <input type="checkbox" name="city" id="cityG"  />
                                        <label for="cityG">
                                            <span>What is <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">diabesity</span>?</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <div class="info">
                                            <p>People who are overweight or obese are more likely to develop Type 2 Diabetes. The term “diabesity” is simply a combination of both conditions. Weight loss can help prevent Type 2 Diabetes. Weight loss improves blood sugar control in people with diabetes and some people can actually come off all their medications for diabetes. Diabesity can be best treated with gradual weight loss under the supervision of medical specialists. This programme is designed to prevent the development of Type 2 Diabetes, however it may also benefit people with existing diabetes. Always consult your doctor before making any changes to your medications.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="block1">
                                        <input type="checkbox" name="city" id="cityH" />
                                        <label for="cityH">
                                            <span>How is <span style="font-weight: bolder;">simply</span>wazan different to the <span style="font-weight: bolder;">simply</span>weight programme?</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <div class="info">
                                            <p>We believe that we have developed the first medical weight management programme exclusively for South Asian and Middle Easterners. This includes all the features of the <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">simply</span>weight programme and incorporates cultural influences and cuisines. If you have concerns about your BMI and you belong to one of these populations, <span style="font-weight: bolder;font-family: 'Conv_MYRIADPRO-BOLD_1',sans-serif;">simply</span>wazan is for you. </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="block">
                                        <input type="checkbox" name="city" id="cityJ" />
                                        <label for="cityJ">
                                            <span>How can an online programme be personalised?</span>
                                        </label>
                                        <div class="info">
                                            <p>While our programme has online features, all of our tutorials and activities involve your full engagement in everyday life. This will not be a programme where you are just sent e-mails and videos each week but rather you will be fully engaged throughout. In addition, our medical experts will be on hand to provide you with personal support and answer individual questions via our forum, webinars and live chats. For our Elite programme members we have dedicated <span>simply</span>weight staff to support them 24/7.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <a href="https://www.simplyweight.co.uk/faq-home" target="_blank"><p class="font">View more</p></a>

